title: The Gunston tapes
brief_description: Contains the best of the Norman Gunston shows. The video includes Warren Beatty and the Qantas air hostess, Hugh Heffner, Muhammad Ali, Keith Moon assaulting “The Little Aussie Bleeder” with a vodka bottle, and the Spaceship Southern Hemisphere.
